Package: Fars
Type: Package
Title:  Fars
Depends: R (>= 3.0.0)
Version: 0.1.0
Author: MvT
Maintainer: MvT <miriamvonthenen@gmx.de>
Description: The package reads in data from the US National Highway Traffic Safety Administration's Fatality Analysis Reporting System (FARS). It provides summaries of the data by months and maps the distribution of accidents per state. 
